channel.title: RsCalifornia 711
channel.description:
http://rscalifornia.com/ - i didnt make site :)
This is more of a out of date beta version, so we'll see how it goes.
Using older source atm: most of this applys:
Gonna miss this...
[center][b]Features:[/b]
Full theiving Full trade Full summoning Pets 100% Nomad 100% Jad Donor & Staff zone Donator ranks with donator symbol Fixed emotes tab Custom quest tab Glacors Armadyl Better pking Fixed some exploits Added token system, you get from boss's npc etc Slayer Tower Most skills work perfectly now Loads of new shops! Custom yell Added teleports such as ::train ::nomad Player ranks scoreboard Tzhaar 100% Theiving Including stalls and pickpocketing Polypore staff Quick prayers work fully Spell book teleports! Castle wars Spirit shield creation 100% Godsword creations Beast graphics 100% Herblore 100% Crafting 100% lobby DFS Spec works Degrading pvp armors Full nex 100% Castle wars! Started on pest control Base!!
And SO MUCH MORE![/left][/center]
Media: [center] [IMG]http://i821.photobucket.com/albums/zz139/zhangboo0o/x22fpy.png[/img] [IMG]http://i821.photobucket.com/albums/zz139/zhangboo0o/pets.png[/img] [IMG]http://i821.photobucket.com/albums/zz139/zhangboo0o/what.png[/img] [IMG]http://i821.photobucket.com/albums/zz139/zhangboo0o/shop.png[/img] [IMG]http://i821.photobucket.com/albums/zz139/zhangboo0o/barrows.png[/img] [IMG]http://i821.photobucket.com/albums/zz139/zhangboo0o/cape.png[/img] [IMG]http://i821.photobucket.com/albums/zz139/zhangboo0o/06.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i821.photobucket.com/albums/zz139/zhangboo0o/33cxmia.png[/img] [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/5mk3nl.png[/img] [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/xdchth.png[/img]
